<span style=\"color: red;\">中国人特質</span>佢地就要花更多時間為中国人呢個身份辯護，亦唔能夠話你<span style=\"color: red;\">屈人做中国人</span>，因為呢一句係非常負面，中共唔想見到。一般會員亦更容易分辨<span style=\"color: red;\">中国人</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下今日捉到幾多連登<span style=\"color: red;\">中国人</span>先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"261aca7b8b81b1f2322508fa672c34de7a9d7f30","tid":364963,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T23:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我的確係中國人，泛民從來都。承認自己係中國人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你地覺得自己係香港人唔係中國人咁威，請你地杯葛泛民既助威遊行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔敢否認<span style=\"color: red;\">中国人</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70114b55a461c93a7ecb7b3750fedeade0ec8cf8","tid":364963,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T23:13:17.000Z","msg":"你地係咪傻撚哂<br />\n<br />\n又要屌鳩人係中國人<br />\n<br />\n又要人參加支持推動中國民主既泛民遊行<br />\n<br />\n又要人支持黃之鋒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/06xzpafc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F06xzpafc&h=dfab81d4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c800b1d7f8149900b3d7846793977719c8478104","tid":364963,"uid":64806,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T23:14:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我的確係中國人，泛民從來都。承認自己係中國人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你地覺得自己係香港人唔係中國人咁威，請你地杯葛泛民既助威遊行</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係唔敢否認<span style=\"color: red;\">中国人</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你地口口聲聲支持既黃之鋒都唔敢否認自己係中國人，你地係咪要聲討佢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla